{"tid":1079204,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊書 做學徒","createTime":"2019-03-26T19:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T14:57:48.000Z","uid":128120,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf749e63800b03d28ebf71b36c3aed5abe57552e","tid":1079204,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:20:50.000Z","msg":"本身番緊pt 一個月都至少一萬<br />\n番12日 14個鐘<br />\n但爸爸身體變差 所以搵左樓下一間腸粉鋪<br />\n老闆直接叫我跟佢學野 做學徒<br />\n比我15000一個月 3個月後17-18000<br />\n但工時應該好長 要開檔關檔<br />\n如果我繼續番原本果度 番20日我都差唔多既錢 但果邊好撚辛苦 得我做野<br />\n但做學徒日日番3個月後先得萬8 但學到一門手藝 仲可以照顧到爸爸 <br />\n我應該點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番原本果度 20日 大約18000<br />\n新工學徒27-8日 18000"},{"pid":"fa3566d9ad499f5719bd8ebfca15250d73109feb","tid":1079204,"uid":120987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:49:59.000Z","msg":"唔好做腸粉鋪，得錢洗返多份PT"},{"pid":"d92f7a8ba141bef44cf0e05bc0b436347c24f824","tid":1079204,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa3566d9ad499f5719bd8ebfca15250d73109feb","tid":1079204,"uid":120987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T19:49:59.000Z","msg":"唔好做腸粉鋪，得錢洗返多份PT"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T20:08:38.000Z","msg":"原本番果度番20日有18000 但學唔到野"},{"pid":"7e7fc1de1582c84c98ef0ba1712545b090c56e8e","tid":1079204,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T20:13:01.000Z","msg":"你讀緊書點返FT?<br />\n讀緊咩?"},{"pid":"2623d07f71d8e57fa07d6089fe9e22439c46d4e6","tid":1079204,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:26:13.000Z","msg":"PT啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n20日<br />\n工時又唔長<br />\n你諗下啦"},{"pid":"c73886214ed64f3effe6afacd94034e4bd854224","tid":1079204,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2623d07f71d8e57fa07d6089fe9e22439c46d4e6","tid":1079204,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T00:26:13